{
  "stem": "18626.11",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 320.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after he left the barrack from the doctor, he went around in the yard, and whoever he could kill with his feet, that man was killing-- all of it his boots-- people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whoever was close by, he knocked them right with the boot in the head.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the right place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That man single-handed-- single foot-- killed dozens of people laying dead on the ground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was Johann Kirsch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he didn't ask me anything else no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Johann Kirsch was right on the thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, after that I was [INAUDIBLE] out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then he says, do you really know Johann Kirsch?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe you just heard about him stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wonder you should come to Johann Kirsch on the stage there where they are placed and show where is Johann Kirsch.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Please, Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Moses, point out where Johann Kirsch is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, when I came to point out where Johann Kirsch, I forgot about the law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I forgot how far I got to stay away from him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My nerves got ahold of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And instead of to show with the finger, I jumped on his neck with my hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I says, this is the murderer!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is Johann Kirsch!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the court right away with the gavel, the main prosecutor knocked to-- with the gavel in court.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the court became with the cameras, with the feeling, with all the things right on the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the prosecutor with the gavel start to stop the commotion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Moses Rutschaisky, if you are going to be-- behave like that, you are going to be taken out of, of the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to see no more action like that and disturbances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Understood?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
